1. Download ie: 'git pull git@github.com:nick8888/mediafrontpage.git'
2. Open mediafrontpage.sh with gedit and edit appropriately
3. Copy css and media folders to $webroot eg /var/www/
4. Copy contents of xbmcwebinterfacedir to xbmc web interface dir (probably /usr/share/xbmc/addons/webinterface.default)
5. Copy mediafrontpage.sh to /etc/cron.hourly/
